org.monome.pages
Class MIDIFader

java.lang.Object
  org.monome.pages.MIDIFader
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable
public class MIDIFader
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable

A thread that behaves like a MIDI fader being moved up or down. It sends out MIDI CC messages from it's starting point to it's ending point and moves at a specified speed. It also updates a monome's leds accordingly as it moves.

Author:
Tom Dinchak
